{"tid":1267751,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大香港意志","createTime":"2019-06-30T05:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T05:58:57.000Z","uid":165234,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4bba71f2991d08c6df3d008720e1084c18692647","tid":1267751,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:00:57.000Z","msg":"歷史上有多種方式推翻當權者包括：<br />\n<br />\n法國大革命- (1789年－1799年)<br />\n自由！平等！博愛！<br />\n<br />\n文化大革命- (1966年－1976年)<br />\n用鮮血和生命保衞黨中央！用鮮血和生命保衞毛主席！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民族主義運動- (1933年&mdash;1945年)<br />\n猶太人問題的最終解決方案！</span><br />\n<br />\n我認為希特拉嘅諗法比毛主席嘅更有用更適合香港<br />\n我抽咗幾句我覺得幾好嘅比大家睇下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">動員民眾不能用愛要用仇恨仇恨是最好的凝聚力</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我們的鬥爭只可能有兩種結果：敵人踏著我們的屍體過去，我們踏著敵人的屍體過去。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我們的思想宣傳必須是人民群眾喜歡的, 而且還能讓最愚蠢的人也能一听就明白。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">德國要麼成為世界強國，要麼不復存在。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tw117.com/mingyan-ren/%E5%B8%8C%E7%89%B9%E5%8B%92/3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tw117.com%2Fmingyan-ren%2F%25E5%25B8%258C%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%258B%2592%2F3%2F&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGrc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=3869f27b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.tw117.com/mingyan-ren/%E5%B8%8C%E7%89%B9%E5%8B%92/3/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大香港意志！</span></span>"},{"pid":"2b38bc88f5bb378513f52d3a0ff82eb318f55a1a","tid":1267751,"uid":54228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:03:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yn7ASQz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYn7ASQz.jpg&h=551baa69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e12de5bad77b7dbd05ded46335fa316827ff9056","tid":1267751,"uid":165234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:03:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一個健康的社會，應該不擇手段掃除邪惡。</span></span>"},{"pid":"5289fed804cebf59b3d89a8e3d6058af5a349f05","tid":1267751,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:14:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國家的安全不能寄託於別人的恩賜上，歷史總是在軍刀上前進，這個世界就是弱肉強食的世界。要生存、要尊嚴，就需要有強大的軍備。</span></span>"},{"pid":"b7c7667ab1d26038853af676e7735056c2da98af","tid":1267751,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:17:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">這些蛆蟲，緊急的時候是懦夫，事後是吹牛家。</span></span>"},{"pid":"4a4c2a33b2de1bb63f247d8fb2cbb99ae563a18a","tid":1267751,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:58:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我們的後代會對我們今天的生活感到恥辱！</span></span>"}]}